<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2>Spas in Jaipur</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:image -->
<figure class="wp-block-image"><img src="https://im.hunt.in/cg/jaipur/City-Guide/Stone-therapy.jpg" alt="Lifestyle in Jaipur" title="Spas in Jaipur"/></figure>
<!-- /wp:image -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Spa is the medium of providing health treatment through water, massages and other therapies. It provides solution to a numerous health problems. It’s main significance lies in providing physical, mental and spiritual peace to the soul and the body. These practices are popular all across the world which involve no pain and provides the best result. Jaipur city is also populated with these Spa centres.&nbsp;<a href="https://www.jaipuronline.in/city-guide/spa-in-jaipur" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Read more</a></p>
